section: ghc-lib
synopsis: GHC now represents string literals in the AST via HText, a GHC
    Modified UTF-8 encoded text, rather than FastString. This makes the AST
    independent of FastString, which is tied to the ghc-the-library internals,
    opening the possibility of pulling the AST out of ghc-the-library.
